Subject: [PATCH] fix: restore local-first project experience for v0.1.14

Disables cloud migration prompts and redirects to preserve the original
local-first experience which is better suited for self-hosted deployments
and agent orchestration workflows.

Changes:
- Change default destination from /workspaces/create to /local-projects
- Disable BetaWorkspacesDialog modal that prompts migration on page load
- Hide migration alert box on kanban dashboard
- Remove unused imports to fix TypeScript build

These changes maintain the preferred local project workflow for
self-hosted installations where users manage local projects rather
than cloud workspaces.
